<http://purl.org/family/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Region Connection Calculus (RCC8) Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Social Relations Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "The Family Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "The Middle-earth ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Time Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Actions as a subclass of events, defined by having an intentional agent."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An ontology for J.R.R. Tolkienʼs legendarium."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An ontology for family relationships."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Events in story plots: occurrences involving characters, places, and time. Includes an event hierarchy, participant roles, and temporal relations."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Instants, intervals, and Allen's 13 temporal relations."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Narrative and literary structure of stories, with a real-world layer (authors, books) and a fictional layer (sections, plot events)."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Non-familial social relations between characters: friendship, enmity, alliance, service, etc."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Place categories and spatial relations for story plots."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "RCC8 spatial relations between regions, encoded with DL-safe OWL axioms."@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Action Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Event Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Place Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Plot Structure Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Social Relations Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The Middle-earth ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The RCC8 ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "The family ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Time Ontology"@en .
<http://purl.org/family/> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "1.0" .
