<http://purl.org/meo/Adan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The Edain (plural form of Adan) are the Men that belong to the Three Houses of Men that came to Beleriand in the elder days. Originally, “Adan” (plural “Edain”) is the Sindarin equivalent of Quenya “Atan” (plural “Atani”) but eventually came to mean this narrow subgroup."@en .
