<http://purl.org/meo/Atan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The Atani (plural form of Atan) are the second born of the Children of Ilúvatar, the Men (i.e. Humans, not male people). They were given many names also by the Eldar."@en .
<http://purl.org/meo/Atan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Adan"@sjn .
